title.rendered: TTE partners with Total Lifting Solutions

content.rendered:
TTE adds Total Lifting Solutions to its extensive brand partner portfolio. Total Lifting Solution (TLS) is one of the UK’s leading bespoke car lift providers and specializes in automated parking systems, underground car park lifts and car turntables. The brand offers customized, innovative lifting solutions using state-of-the-art engineering, robust and superior quality materials that are built and rigorously tested in their factory.

James Edge, Managing Director, TLS was greeted by Dilip Sharma, ECIG Executive Vice President on his visit to the Technical & Trading Est. (TTE) headquarters. Both partners signed the exclusive distributorship agreement and shared thoughts and insights on the way forward.
